-- Virgo Engineers to Offer 13.4 Million Shares in India Initial Share Sale
-- Chitra Somayaji
-- 2010-07-12T04:25:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/virgo-engineers-to-offer-13-4-million-shares-in-india-initial-share-sale.html

          
          
             Virgo Engineers Ltd. will offer 13.4
million shares to investors in an initial public offering in
India, according to a draft sale document.  
 The sale, to be managed by IDFC capital Ltd. and Edelweiss
Capital Ltd., will include 10.7 million new shares and 2.69
million shares offered by existing holders, according to the
July 8 prospectus posted on Edelweissâ€™s website.  
          
          


  


        